{"TopicId":184883,"ForumId":107,"TopicTitle":"IVA view does not follow rotation","CreatedByName":"marce","CreatedById":110351,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-30T19:35:48Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"marce","CreatedById":110351,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-30T19:35:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust got Breaking Ground and started to play around with the robotics parts.\u003Cbr\u003E\nPut a lander can on pistons, hinges and a servo. Up/down \u0026amp; left/right works fine, but when rotating the IVA view does not follow the rotation.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nNavball does move\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nAfter a timewarp the camera snaps to the correct position\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nTried to make a quick video (sorry for the poor quality but it should still show the issue)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022344\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/c3rZqO0HEiM?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022459\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"nestor","CreatedById":163018,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-30T20:03:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHey, thanks for the report.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe can\u0027t reproduce this bug.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCould you try without mods and see if the issue\u00A0is still happening?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Serenity","CreatedById":179192,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-31T02:52:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs this the stock lander can?Sry i am tired and my eyes are blurry \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u00A0.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"marce","CreatedById":110351,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-31T07:47:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223608218\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184883\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221559246631\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022163018\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022nestor\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 hours ago, nestor said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHey, thanks for the report.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe can\u0027t reproduce this bug.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCould you try without mods and see if the issue\u00A0is still happening?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOf course. Just tried without all mods (no change) and then after verifying local files (2 files were re-downloaded) and without mods\u00A0=\u0026gt; \u003Cstrong\u003Estill the same issue\u003C/strong\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI haven\u0027t used KSP in quite a while so I\u0027m a little out of touch: is there some debug log/mode I can activate and send you?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223608494\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184883\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221559271159\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179192\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Boyster\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, Boyster said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs this the stock lander can?Sry i am tired and my eyes are blurry \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u00A0.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, all stock except for a custom flag (but that shouldn\u0027t be an issue I guess).\u003Cbr\u003E\nActually, I think it\u0027s not your eyes but YT hating my video and restricting it to 480p\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:wink:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ZodiusInfuser","CreatedById":76163,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-31T09:47:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI was able to reproduce this in 1 minute. Happens if the pod is not on the root side of the craft. Tested with the following craft. Pod closest to the camera is the root.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022N0VzygH.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/N0VzygH.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003Eg\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso observe that when the pod on the root side does rotate, the IVA of the second pod rotates around that axis. That\u0027s how I was able to get this out-of-body shot of an IVA view seeing both command pods.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022qHHbR6G.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/qHHbR6G.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003Eg\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"marce","CreatedById":110351,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-31T10:18:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/76163-zodiusinfuser/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002276163\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/76163-zodiusinfuser/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@ZodiusInfuser\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0awesome, thanks for figuring this out!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n@SQUAD: if you need anything else please notify me, otherwise I suppose you have enough information to pinpoint the issue.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Just Jim","CreatedById":148725,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-31T13:50:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223608705\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184883\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221559296069\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002276163\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ZodiusInfuser\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, ZodiusInfuser said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI was able to reproduce this in 1 minute. Happens if the pod is not on the root side of the craft. Tested with the following craft. Pod closest to the camera is the root.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/N0VzygH.png\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022N0VzygH.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/N0VzygH.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003Eg\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso observe that when the pod on the root side does rotate, the IVA of the second pod rotates around that axis. That\u0027s how I was able to get this out-of-body shot of an IVA view seeing both command pods.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/qHHbR6G.png\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022qHHbR6G.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/qHHbR6G.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003Eg\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nQuestion: Are you running any mods?\u003Cbr\u003E\nAnd can you possibly\u00A0attach a craft file for this, or pm one to me, please?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-05-31T13:51:53Z\u0022 title=\u002205/31/2019 01:51  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EMay 31, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Just Jim\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ZodiusInfuser","CreatedById":76163,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-31T14:03:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223608825\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184883\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221559310616\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022148725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Just Jim\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 minutes ago, Just Jim said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nQuestion: Are you running any mods?\u003Cbr\u003E\nAnd can you possibly\u00A0attach a craft file for this, or pm one to me, please?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, Infernal Robotics (being a dev for that mod), but will test without it tonight after work and send the craft I have if it still occurs. Interestingly I did the same test with IR rotational parts and there was no problem\u00A0(other than autostruts from the landing legs to the pods screwing things up).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/110351-marce/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022110351\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/110351-marce/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@marce\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0can send you his craft in the mean-time?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"marce","CreatedById":110351,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-31T14:23:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223608839\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184883\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221559311429\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002276163\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ZodiusInfuser\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n18 minutes ago, ZodiusInfuser said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, Infernal Robotics (being a dev for that mod), but will test without it tonight after work and send the craft I have if it still occurs. Interestingly I did the same test with IR rotational parts and there was no problem\u00A0(other than autostruts from the landing legs to the pods screwing things up).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/110351-marce/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022110351\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/110351-marce/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@marce\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0can send you his craft in the mean-time?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/148725-just-jim/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022148725\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/148725-just-jim/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Just Jim\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0pm\u0027d you a simple craft which shows the issue on my machine.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Just Jim","CreatedById":148725,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-31T14:50:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223608851\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184883\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221559312582\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110351\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022marce\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n25 minutes ago, marce said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/148725-just-jim/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022148725\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/148725-just-jim/\u0022 id=\u0022ips_uid_3435_4\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Just Jim\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0pm\u0027d you a simple craft which shows the issue on my machine.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOK,\u00A0I got it... and yeah, I think I\u00A0see what\u0027s going on now. I can\u00A0take it from here. Thank you all for your help!!!\u00A0\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}